
<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About SRMHacknHub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header Section -->
 
    <div class="container">
        <main>
            <section class="about-hero">
                <h2>Welcome to SRMHacknHub</h2>
                <p>SRMHacknHub is a community-driven platform dedicated to fostering innovation and collaboration among students and professionals. Our mission is to provide a space where individuals can come together to share ideas, work on projects, and develop their skills.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="about-content">
                <div class="mission-vision">
                    <div class="mission">
                        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                        <p>At SRMHacknHub, we aim to:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Encourage creativity and innovation</li>
                            <li>Provide resources and support for project development</li>
                            <li>Facilitate networking and collaboration</li>
                            <li>Host events and workshops to enhance learning</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <section>
                    <h2>Join Us</h2>
                    <p>Whether you are a student, a professional, or simply someone with a passion for technology, SRMHacknHub welcomes you. Join us today and be a part of a vibrant and dynamic community.</p>
                </section>

            </section>

            <section class="faq-section">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                
                <div class="faq-container">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <h3>What services does SRMHacknHub offer?</h3>
                            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>We offer comprehensive software solutions including enterprise resource planning, customer relationship management, and custom software development.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <h3>How do I get technical support?</h3>
                            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>Technical support is available 24/7 through our helpdesk, email support, or phone support. Premium customers have access to dedicated support teams.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <h3>What industries do you serve?</h3>
                            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>We serve various industries including healthcare, finance, retail, manufacturing, and technology sectors.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <h3>Do you offer custom solutions?</h3>
                            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <p>Yes, we offer customized solutions tailored to your specific business needs and requirements.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
</body>
</html>